    "en": "Then she unfreezes.",
    "zh": "然後她解凍了。",
    "ja": "そして彼女は解凍する。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:02:35",
    "en": "Oh, and then Elsa woke up the magical spirits,",
    "zh": "喔，然後Elsa喚醒了魔法精靈，",
    "ja": "ああ、それからエルサは魔法の精霊を目覚めさせた、"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:02:37",
    "en": "and we were forced out of our kingdom, now our only hope is to find the truth about the past,",
